<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />新年第一天如果能过得舒舒服服的，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就会觉得这一年肯定诸事顺利，对不对？<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="4" />呢？<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉今天开心吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已经把去年的日记本收拾好了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />从今天开始我要换一本来写。<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要继续在新日记里填满回忆！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你会帮我的吧？<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天气这么晴好，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />稍微放纵一下自己，应该没什么问题吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如说……<delay20 />
多吃一块年糕！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />发生了这么多事情，<delay8 />
有喜有悲的一年<delay8 />就这样过去了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年我一定得努力，<delay8 />
要让自己做到笑口常开。<pageBreak />俗话说能笑是福嘛！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />来吧！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
笑一个，<delay8 />笑一个！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">趁这个机会，<delay8 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是先把今年的目标
定下来比较好？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是要把<tag a="135" b="8" arg="0xcd00" />钻研透彻吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />制作一份<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />的<delay8 />
品尝指南地图好像也很不错！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
你已经<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />决定了今年的目标吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>